text: b"So much for my HIMYM marathon viewing session. Guess I'll go to bed. Get it together Netflix. And Amazon."
b"Ugh. RT: @GilFalso Looks like Amazon's cloud storage is currently down. This explains Netflix and other outages - http://t.co/u7iNtsAh33 \xe2\x80\xa6"
b'Before I turn 30 I wanna... Finish training and run the NYC Marathon! @paddywhiskeyus #swy30'
b'Finally - looks like Chromecast might make it outside of the US! Thanks for the tip, @GilFalso! http://t.co/5ui5akYKGE'
b"@GilFalso You yanks and your university football and sports obsessions. Something I just don't get. As you were."

b'Here because my new job says Twitter participation is a "good idea". Up to now, I\'ve only read, not participated in Twitter.'
